snippet.title: Snailiad Video Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Join the Snailiad Discord! https://discord.gg/pCYNfmDCZQ 

Play Snailiad: http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/573352

I played through my game, Snailiad!  It's not a perfect playthrough, but it'll show you the basic path through the game :-)  Sorry about the low video framerate.  

Although this is the basic path through the game, there may be alternate paths...  and you may be able to win much faster than this ;-)

Here's the official map I made: http://auriplane.net/gamemap.png

Here's another map, this one made by the Newgrounds user alphasoldier: http://bbsimg.ngfiles.com/3/22973000/ngbbs4e0cc10a4ea43.gif

_@__v!
